ascend_skill.desc:
When using Catchy Hook, increase Ayaka's Attack by 20% (up to 40%) for that battle.
Catchy Hook has a cooldown time of 1 turn before it can be used. Increase the cooldown time each time Catchy Hook is used (up to 3 turns).
ascend_skill.name: Opening Act

ascend_skill.desc:
At the start of battle, grant Costar to the ally with the highest Attack for 3 turns (prioritizing Assassins and Sweepers).
Increase that ally's critical rate by 15%.
ascend_skill.name: Hard Rock

ascend_skill.desc: When using Catchy Hook, increase targeted ally's damage by 30% for 2 turns.
ascend_skill.name: Crescendo Shout

ascend_skill.desc: Increase the skill levels of Distortion and Catchy Hook by 3.
ascend_skill.name: Amplifier

ascend_skill.desc:
Highlight Enhanced: Increase effect duration to 6 ally actions.
Fill the Highlight gauge to 60%, and decrease Highlight activation cooldown for all other allies by 1 turn.
ascend_skill.name: Spotlight

ascend_skill.desc: Increase the skill levels of Unison Notes and Thief Tactics by 3.
ascend_skill.name: Shredding

ascend_skill.desc:
At the start of battle, Catchy Hook can be used immediately. Cooldown time is permanently decreased to 1 turn and won't increase.
Every time Catchy Hook is used, increase the party's damage by 20% (up to 2 stacks).
ascend_skill.name: Spirit of Rock

highlight_skill.desc:
For 4 ally actions, increase the party's damage by 45.5%/50.1%/48.3%/52.9%.
While active, fill the Highlight gauge by 10% after an ally acts (up to 40%).
highlight_skill.name: Highlight

normal_skill.desc:
Deal Electric damage to all foes equal to 85.4%/94.2%/90.6%/99.4% of Attack. 80% chance to inflict Shock on the main target for 2 turns.
If an ally has Costar, deal bonus Electric damage to the main target equal to 83.3%/91.8%/88.4%/96.9% of that ally's Attack (1 hit).
normal_skill.name: Distortion

normal_skill.desc:
Grant Costar to 1 ally, and increase their Attack by 24% of Ayaka's Attack (up to 1220/1345/1295/1420) for 3 turns.
Only 1 ally can be a Costar at a time.
normal_skill.name: Unison Notes

normal_skill.desc:
Immediately activate the selected ally's Highlight and increase its damage by 78.1%/86.1%/82.9%/90.9%.
This skill does not affect the target's Highlight cooldown time, even if it activates a Highlight.
normal_skill.name: Catchy Hook

passive_skill.desc:
When an ally uses a Highlight, increase target's Attack by 24.0% for 1 turn.
When the target has Costar, increase effect by 1.5 times.
passive_skill.name: Backing Track

passive_skill.desc: After an ally uses a Highlight, the ally with the lowest HP recovers HP equal to 15.0% of Ayaka's Attack + 1350.
passive_skill.name: Chorus Effect
